Names: CJ Parham and Ethan Turner


1.	Precondition: Less than 5 active missiles on the screen
Action: User right-clicks or presses spacebar
Postcondition: Missile launch gets initiated


2.	Precondition: No active ships
Action: System initiates a ship launch
Postcondition: New active ships appear on the screen


3.	Precondition: Active ship going across the screen
Action: Ship goes off the screen
Postcondition: System removes the ship from being active


4.	Precondition: Game is actively running
Action: “Hit” count reaches 10, OR user clicks left mouse button, OR user clicks the escape button, OR the user has not initiated a missile launch in the last 5 minutes
Postcondition: Game ends


5.	Precondition: Active ships and missiles launched
Action: Ship gets hit by missile
Postcondition: An “explosion” is shown at the point of impact, the missile and ship are removed, and the “hit” count updates
